preference.name: CondValResultSummary.SUMMARY_REGISTEREDTO
preference.preference_description: Indicates the business object type to which the CondValResult summary style sheet can be applied. The CondValData object contains verification rules that are used by the Validation Manager checker. The setting determines how detail information about the BOM grading result displays in the Detail Information pane in Structure Manager.
